{"data": [{"id": "4742111", "title": "Why The Latest Corporate Earnings May Fuel Market Optimism In 2025", "description": "<p></p> <p><strong>Greg Bonnell:</strong> US markets have continued to climb to record highs this year, the S&amp;P 500 and the NASDAQ Composite both gaining another 5% in November alone. Well, my next guest says this is no longer a mega tech rally. So what is happening in the equity markets right now? Damian Fernandes, Managing Director and Portfolio Manager with TD Asset Management, joins us. Great to have you back on the program, Damian.</p> <p><strong>Damian Fernandes:</strong> Thanks, Greg. Always a pleasure to be on.</p> <p><strong>Greg Bonnell:</strong> All right. So here we are. We're in the last trading month of the year. Stocks have been on a record run. We just got through an earnings season. It's time to pick your brain as to what's going on.</p> <p><strong>Damian Fernandes:</strong> You know what? It's so much more enjoyable coming here on a bull market. It's the Christmas season. It's the gift of giving. And who doesn't love a big rip-roaring bull market to end the year?</p> <p><strong>Greg Bonnell:</strong> So let's talk about what got us here, what is going on, and, well, maybe we can dig into earnings, too. I mean, we're past the bulk of it in the States.</p> <p><strong>Damian Fernandes:</strong> Sure, yeah.</p> <p><strong>Greg Bonnell:</strong> Did it show you something to justify what we're seeing in the markets?</p> <p><strong>Damian Fernandes:</strong> Yeah, so if I split that into two things-- what got us here. What got us here is actually a pretty favorable backdrop. I know that might seem -- might seem difficult just because it seems so volatile politically, geopolitically, macro. But when you look at the fundamentals that drive stocks, earnings for 2024 are going to be up about 10%. We just had-- we had a pretty good earnings quarter.</p> <p>Last year, inflation was still running hot. Central banks had started easing. But as we've</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742111-why-the-latest-corporate-earnings-may-fuel-market-optimism-in-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 21:10:00"}, {"id": "4742098", "title": "ETB: Providing A Distribution Rate Of ~8.5% With Monthly Pay", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810174/image_1445810174.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Saving time\" data-id=\"1445810174\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1055px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810174/image_1445810174.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810174/image_1445810174.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810174/image_1445810174.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810174/image_1445810174.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810174/image_1445810174.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810174/image_1445810174.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810174/image_1445810174.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810174/image_1445810174.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Written by Nick Ackerman, co-produced by Stanford Chemist.</em></p> <p><b>Eaton Vance Tax-Managed Buy-Write Income Fund</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ETB\" title=\"Eaton Vance Tax-Managed Buy-Write Income Fund\">ETB</a></span>) is a closed-end fund that provides exposure to an S&amp;P 500-esque portfolio while utilizing a call-writing strategy. The fund has performed</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810174/image_1445810174.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742098-etb-providing-a-distribution-rate-of-8-5-percent-with-monthly-pay", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 20:56:19"}, {"id": "4742110", "title": "Central Bank Gold Statistics: October 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Gold ingots and coins close up\" data-id=\"145158250\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5224px\" height=\"4016px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Anthony Bradshaw</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><span>Central bank gold buying ramps up in October</span></h2> <h3>India, Turkey and Poland lead net buying y-t-d</h3> <ul> <li>Central banks <a href=\"https://www.gold.org/goldhub/data/gold-reserves-by-country\" rel=\"noopener\">reported</a> 60t of net purchases this month \u2013 the highest amount recorded y-t-d<sup>1</sup> </li> <li>The Reserve Bank of India (RBI) led the</li> </ul>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145158250/image_145158250.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742110-central-bank-gold-statistics-october-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 20:50:00"}, {"id": "4742096", "title": "Udemy: Rating Downgrade As Growth Continues To Decelerate", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1690435627/image_1690435627.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Students sitting in class at technical college\" data-id=\"1690435627\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1015px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1690435627/image_1690435627.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1690435627/image_1690435627.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1690435627/image_1690435627.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1690435627/image_1690435627.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1690435627/image_1690435627.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1690435627/image_1690435627.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1690435627/image_1690435627.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1690435627/image_1690435627.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">10'000 Hours/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Summary</h2> <p>I downgraded Udemy (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UDMY\" title=\"Udemy, Inc.\">UDMY</a></span>) to a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4723542-udemy-rating-downgrade-on-poor-operating-trends-change-business-strategy\">hold rating</a> in late September, as I did not have confidence that UDMY could continue to perform strongly, especially with the change in business model. One of the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1690435627/image_1690435627.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742096-udemy-rating-downgrade-as-growth-continues-to-decelerate", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 20:39:17"}, {"id": "4742093", "title": "Russell 2000: IWM Vs. UWM - 2 Ways To Invest In Small-Cap America", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319467815/image_1319467815.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Man putting coin into rising stack of coins with plant.\" data-id=\"1319467815\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"965px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319467815/image_1319467815.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319467815/image_1319467815.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319467815/image_1319467815.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319467815/image_1319467815.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319467815/image_1319467815.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319467815/image_1319467815.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319467815/image_1319467815.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319467815/image_1319467815.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andranik Hakobyan/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Russell 2000 (RUT) is a small cap index which represents the 2000 smaller stocks in the Russell 2000 index.</p> <p>Small cap stocks have been playing catch up recently with the larger cap segment</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319467815/image_1319467815.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742093-russell-2000-iwm-vs-uwm-2-ways-invest-small-cap-america", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 20:35:20"}, {"id": "4742089", "title": "Vinci/Compass Merger: Information Missing, Remains A Cautious Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163172103/image_163172103.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Antique brass compas and ocean\" data-id=\"163172103\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163172103/image_163172103.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163172103/image_163172103.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163172103/image_163172103.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163172103/image_163172103.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163172103/image_163172103.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163172103/image_163172103.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163172103/image_163172103.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163172103/image_163172103.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Gary S Chapman</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Vinci Partners (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VINP\" title=\"Vinci Partners Investments Ltd.\">VINP</a></span>) reported 3Q24 results and held a conference to announce its combination with Compass, a Chilean asset manager.</p> <p>I covered the Compass merger with a critical view when it was announced in <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4678797-vinci-stock-still-buy-after-acquiring-compass-but-with-more-caution\">March 2024</a>. Although</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163172103/image_163172103.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742089-vinci-compass-merger-information-missing-remains-cautious-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 20:20:32"}, {"id": "4742083", "title": "Pure Storage Q3: Sell This Spike (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885300378/image_885300378.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Side view of woman working in illuminated server room\" data-id=\"885300378\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885300378/image_885300378.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885300378/image_885300378.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885300378/image_885300378.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885300378/image_885300378.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885300378/image_885300378.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885300378/image_885300378.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885300378/image_885300378.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885300378/image_885300378.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Erik Isakson</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>2024 is nearing its end, and with stock markets continuing to hover around all-time highs, I continue to be incredibly cautious about what I choose to invest in and retain in my portfolio. Active portfolio management, in my view, will be key</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885300378/image_885300378.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742083-pure-storage-q3-sell-this-spike-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 20:02:13"}, {"id": "4742080", "title": "Texas Instruments: A Hold Amid Solid Fundamentals And Growth Prospects", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Texas Instruments Inc (TI) HQ in Silicon Valley\" data-id=\"1173014771\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5902px\" height=\"3937px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Sundry Photography</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Texas Instruments' (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TXN\" title=\"Texas Instruments Incorporated\">TXN</a></span>) current valuation seems fair relative to its peers. I believe its focus on long-term technology developmen